            <div class="answer-area"></div>
        </li>
        <li>
            השלימו:
            <div class="ltr">א. x = 5.7 → x × 0.01 = ?  ב. y = 120 → y ÷ 1000 = ?</div>
            <span class="answer-line"></span>
        </li>
    </ol>
</section>

